Use the standard library
This is how to sort_array of arr:
  Remember that result is []
  Remember that used is []

  Do this arr's length times:
    Remember that best_index is 0
    Remember that best_value is nothing
    Remember that found is no

    Do this arr's length times:
      Remember that i is item 0 in used
      Decrease item 0 in used by 1
      When found is no, then:
        Remember that best_index is i
        Remember that best_value is item i in arr
        Remember that found is yes
      But, if not:
        When item i in arr is less than best_value, then:
          Remember that best_index is i
          Remember that best_value is item i in arr
        End when
      End when
    End do

    Add result to best_value

    Remember that next_used is []
    Do this arr's length times:
      Remember that j is item 0 in used
      Decrease item 0 in used by 1
      When j is not best_index, then:
        Add next_used to j
      End when
    End do
    Remember that used is next_used
  End do

  The answer is result
Now you know